Le nto iyinkinga kabi ngoba umuntu uthi sekufanele akhiphe imali yokukhokha kodwa uthole ukuthi ubhizi ukhuluma neselula anisakwazi ukuyiqoqa kahle imali yomshayeli nilinde yena ukuthi aqede. Ake sizifundiseni ukwenza into eyodwa ngesikhathi siyiqede bese senza okunye. Ukhuluma neselula udlulisa imali uze wenze namaphutha. Uma kungena ucingo usekhumbini ehambayo akuthi uma sekuqoqwa imali umtshele abuye akuthinte mhlawumbe ngemumva kwemizuzu emihlanu ukuze uyikhiphe kahle imali okhokha ngayo. Abanye ubathola befake ama-head set khona ekhumbini agcine engasezwa lutho uma kukhulunywa ngemali. Asiyiyekeni bakwethu le mikhuba yokusebenzisa amaselula emakhumbini ngoba kugcina sekuphazamiseka nabanye abantu abasuke begibele.  Edmund Ngcobo EHammarsdale